cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a system for developing an automatic speech recognizer for Cantonese, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with speech recognition, which is a sound-based task. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are relevant categories as the paper uses transfer learning, a machine learning technique, to improve the performance of the ASR system. 
- cs.SI (Speech and Audio Processing) is also a possible category as the paper deals with speech recognition and transfer learning, which are both related to speech and audio processing.
